msgid "Tips and Tricks"
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/communications/newsletter.md:59
msgid ""
"The Mailchimp editor is not entirely user-friendly.  Formatting changes "
"may appear in the edit window but not in the preview document. The "
"easiest workaround for this is to:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/communications/newsletter.md:60
msgid "Copy and paste text in the Mailchimp editor."
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/communications/newsletter.md:61
msgid "Select all text in the Mailchimp editor and click Clear Styles."
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/communications/newsletter.md:62
msgid "Select all text and set font to Arial 12 point."
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/communications/newsletter.md:63
msgid ""
"Select the title (\"Carpentries Clippings, <date>\") and set font to 18 "
"pt bold."
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/communications/newsletter.md:64
msgid ""
"Select each subheading one by one (Highlights from the Carpentries "
"Community Calendar, Community News, etc.) and set font to 16 pt bold."
msgstr ""

#: ../../topic_folders/communications/newsletter.md:65
msgid "Select each item heading one by one and set font to 14 point regular."
msgstr ""

